These regulations implement the changes made to the HEA by the Higher Education Amendments of 1992 (Pub. L. 102-325)
and the Higher Education Technical Amendments of 1993 (Pub. L. 103-208).




On January 24, 1994 the Secretary published a notice of proposed rulemaking (NPRM) for this program in the 

