State review standards for referred institutions (pages 3611-3613);

Procedures for the disapproval by the Secretary of State review standards (pages 3613-3614);

Procedures regarding SPRE reviews of referred institutions (page 3614);

Peer reviews of institutions (pages 3614-3615);

