None.



Standard in Proposed  667.21(a)(11) Governing Market, Job Availability, and Licensing Standards





Comments: 

A few commenters suggested that the Secretary should expand this standard. The commenters were concerned that the
standard does not specify the geographical scope of the labor market information to be provided, nor does it specify
