 600.31 

Change in ownership resulting in a change of control. 


(a) 

General. 

(1) An institution that undergoes a change of ownership that results in a change of control ceases to qualify as an eligible
institution upon the change of ownership and control. A change of ownership that results in a change in control includes
any change by which a person who has or thereby acquires an ownership interest in the entity that owns the institution
